Scenario
Luke is a student at the University of Charlotte. He has already had one internship at a game company but would like to redo his resume and get a few tips for interviews.
Luke decides to use the Career Center but is unable to get any tips about interviews. They also tell him his resume is well put together. Luke is discouraged as he really wanted to get a better resume and tips for interviews.
 
 User Story
 As a student, Luke wants to be able to look for an internship and resume helper so that he can apply to get an internship.
